title: 12/16/20 DPS BEST OF
itunes:title: 12/16/20 DPS BEST OF
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP reacts to Giannis' contract extension. Is his decision to stay in Milwaukee a good move for the NBA as a league? Dan also expresses his frustration with the newly released College Football Playoff Rankings. Why doesn't the committee give non Power 5 schools a chance. We're joined by Sports Illustrated's Chris Mannix, SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey, and Projected No.1 pick/Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence.
